column5: Looking for a little help finding some lakes or rivers along Lake Superior for specks, my health is not so good so I can't portage my canoe; anything close to a road would be very helpful. I'm going May 12th. Thanks for any help.
I'm from Michigan, not sure what pm's are. Sorry
